  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I don't want to see a tab bar while editing the photo so that I could be fully focused on that process.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Fun Android bug that keeps showing a tab bar above keyboard while a user is editing userpick or name. Tab bar should be hidden. Check iOS build for reference.  \r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n<img width=\"428\" alt=\"screenshot 2018-04-11 11 10 45\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/38607479-0874fbd2-3d79-11e8-9946-3a61b2180937.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![image 2018-04-11 11 08 55](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6559881/38607372-ba737684-3d78-11e8-93d1-1295365817dd.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open profile tab\r\n- Tap Edit in the right top corner\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly 10.05.2018\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n",
